com.aliyun.oss.model

类 RoutingRule.Redirect

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aliyun.oss.model.RoutingRule.Redirect
  • 封闭类:
    RoutingRule

    public static class RoutingRule.Redirect
extends Object
    Container element that provides instructions for redirecting the request. You can redirect requests to another host, or another page, or you can specify another protocol to use.
